divs: sighting detailsi was in prairieville louisiana on insurance business on september 09, 2008. i was taking digital photos of a house that was damaged from hurricane "gustav". i did not see or hear anything unusual at the time. a few months later, i was analysing my photos and observed a stange object in the top left corner of one of them. it was perplexing because i could not explain what it was. i have posted it on youtube @ http:\\www.youtube.com\watch?v=xvit2xz26bs i will attach the original, unedited, unenhanced digital photo for you review. please let me know your official findings once a conclusion has been made. thanks. troy nelsen
Summary: DAYTIME UFO SIGHTING IN PRAIRIEVILLE LOUISIANA ON 09-09-08 WHILE WORKING AFTER HURRICANE GUSTAV HIT THE AREA.
